16 follows:
17 Section 9101. A. The Department of Public Safety shall
18 establish and maintain a Mental Wellness Division to provide mental
19 wellness services and programs to public safety personnel and
20 retirees thereof to promote good mental wellness. The Commissioner
21 of Public Safety shall appoint the Director of the Mental Wellness
22 Division.
23 B. The Director of the Mental Wellness Division shall report to
24 the Commissioner. All current and former employees of the Mental
